OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fwith patchy mist and low cloud. Chilly
OL,9,Fnight in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FOnce again a dry, warm and
OL,12,Fsunny day after any mist or low cloud
OL,13,Fclears in the morning. Breezy at times
OL,14,Faround coasts and exposed higher
OL,15,Fground.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,18,Fdry, bright and warm on Friday but
OL,19,Fcloudier with the chance of a shower
OL,20,Flater. Cooler and cloudier over the
OL,21,Fweekend with a chance of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
